description:
Danny welcomes the stunning Cynthia Bailey (The Real Housewives of Atlanta) to Everything Iconic. They talk about the explosive reunion, her relationship with Nene, thoughts on the new girls, her Seagram's Peach Bellinis, and SO much more. So sit back, relax, and #CHill while you listen to Cynthia break down this season of RHOA.
